1d:T42a,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as an end cap component (not the nail itself) for elastic titanium intramedullary nails. The brochure description 'End caps for elastic titanium nails' and SKU example 'End Caps (Nailing System)' confirm this is an accessory/instrument component. Material TAV (Ti-6Al-4V) is standard for such components. The specification 'Self-retaining T25 Star drive recess' indicates the cap has a star drive interface for insertion/removal and self-retaining mechanism to secure to the nail. The current title 'Nail Cap For Elastic Titanium Nail' is accurate but could be clearer by using 'End Caps' (plural, as these are catalog items sold in sets) and explicitly naming the system brand. Entity type is 'instrument' as end caps are removable components/accessories used with implants, not implantable devices themselves. Elastic nails are predominantly used in pediatric long bone fractures. High confidence due to consistent internal evidence. Recommend rename to improve clarity for clinical users searching for end cap components.18:["$","$L1c",null,{"product":{"product_name":"CLAVO Nail Cap For Elastic Titanium Nail","product_name_display":"CLAVO End Caps for Elastic Titanium Nails","sku_code":"MT-ET0615000","product_family":"CLAVO Nail Cap For Elastic Titanium Nail","product_family_display":"CLAVO Nail Cap For Elastic Titanium Nail","slug":"clavo-nail-cap-for-elastic-titanium-nail","images":[{"id":"4e384cebdb84","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c17bd504841ec9248cfabb/cover_6899289c.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Destiknee Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":208705,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:55:44.917719+00:00","source":"division_fallback","width":1600,"height":1600}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"agile-ortho/brochures/clavo-pfrn.pdf","seo_meta_title":"CLAVO End Caps for Elastic Titanium Nails | Meril Orthopedics Trauma Implants - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Meril'